original_title: WCW Clash of The Champions XIV: Dixie Dynamite
overview: Scott Steiner challenges "The Nature Boy" Ric Flair for the WCW World Heavyweight Championship. Sting & Lex Luger collide with the WCW World Tag Team Champions Doom. The Four Horsemen take on The Renegade Warriors in tag team action. Missy Hyatt competes in an Inter-Gender Arm Wrestling Contest against Paul E. Dangerously and more.
title: WCW Clash of The Champions XIV: Dixie Dynamite
